data.description: Large home on 2.79 acres located in Rainbow Acres. This home offers 2175 sq ft with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms plus a large bonus room that can be used as an office, den or 4th bedroom. The kitchen has stainless steel appliance and overlooks the large Livingroom with a stone fireplace. The sizeable screened in back porch offers a generous view of the back yard. This home is located conveniently to everything Dunnellon has to offer. Including the Rainbow River and waterfront dining. Dunnellon is full of history, shops and outdoor activities to enjoy.
